re was never an intention to show disrespect towards any religious group or belief \\u2026 [Jolly] is not the first artist to make a reference to what is a world-famous work of art.\", \"from\": 3644, \"to\": 3831, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an intention\", \"from\": 3669, \"to\": 3681}, {\"ngram\": \"any religious group\", \"from\": 3709, \"to\": 3728}, {\"ngram\": \"belief\", \"from\": 3732, \"to\": 3738}, {\"ngram\": \"the first artist\", \"from\": 3756, \"to\": 3772}, {\"ngram\": \"a reference\", \"from\": 3781, \"to\": 3792}, {\"ngram\": \"a world-famous work\", \"from\": 3804, \"to\": 3823}, {\"ngram\": \"art\", \"from\": 3827, \"to\": 3830}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From Andy Warhol to 'The Simpsons,' many have done it before him.\\\"\", \"from\": 3832, \"to\": 3898, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3837, \"end\": 3848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Warhol\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2811649965518496e-53, \"text\": \"Andy Warhol\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Warhol\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Warhol\"}, {\"begin\": 3853, \"end\": 3865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Simpsons\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.547640020673397e-16, \"text\": \"The Simpsons\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Simpsons\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Simpsons\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, in a conflicting statement, JollytoldFrench broadcaster BFMTV on Sunday \\\"That wasn't my inspiration and that should be pretty obvious.\", \"from\": 3900, \"to\": 4043, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a conflicting statement\", \"from\": 3912, \"to\": 3935}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 3974, \"to\": 3980}, {\"ngram\": \"my inspiration\", \"from\": 3994, \"to\": 4008}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is Dionysus arriving on a table.\