 \"from\": 4259, \"to\": 4263}, {\"ngram\": \"the jewels\", \"from\": 4286, \"to\": 4296}, {\"ngram\": \"the father\", \"from\": 4312, \"to\": 4322}, {\"ngram\": \"S\\u00e9quana\", \"from\": 4326, \"to\": 4333}, {\"ngram\": \"the goddess\", \"from\": 4335, \"to\": 4346}, {\"ngram\": \"the river Seine\", \"from\": 4350, \"to\": 4365}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The idea was to depict a big pagan celebration, linked to the gods of Olympus, and thus the Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 4367, \"to\": 4469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4437, \"end\": 4444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Olympus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.761880029316068e-14, \"text\": \"Olympus\", \"types\": [\"Q8502\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Olympus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Olympus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The idea\", \"from\": 4367, \"to\": 4375}, {\"ngram\": \"a big pagan celebration\", \"from\": 4390, \"to\": 4413}, {\"ngram\": \"the gods\", \"from\": 4425, \"to\": 4433}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Olympic Committee also took tosocial mediato address the controversy.\", \"from\": 4471, \"to\": 4558, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4475, \"end\": 4506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tosocial mediato address\", \"from\": 4517, \"to\": 4541}, {\"ngram\": \"the controversy\", \"from\": 4542, \"to\": 4557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In the daily press briefing, the Organising Committee said that there was never any intention to show disrespect towards any religious group or belief,\\\" the statement said.\", \"from\": 4560, \"to\": 4733, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"th